genresAdvancedInfo.name: pinoy edm
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Pinoy EDM, or Electronic Dance Music, is a fast-paced and energetic genre that has gained popularity in the Philippines in recent years. It is characterized by its heavy use of synthesizers, drum machines, and other electronic instruments, and is often associated with the club and rave scenes. Pinoy EDM is known for its pulsing beats and catchy hooks, and is a favorite among dance enthusiasts.
